ing campaigns finally as a marketing campaign prepares for its launch all the issues addressed in this and earlier units must come together in a formalized document  the comprehensive marketing plan unit  time advisory completing this unit should take approximately  hours ☐    subunit   hours ☐    subunit   hours ☐    subunit   hours ☐    subunit   hours ☐    subunit   hours unit learning outcomes upon successful completion of this unit you will be able to identify and describe customer satisfaction factors that affect marketing efforts   identify components of social marketing   explain how to adjust to cultural factors that affect marketing efforts and   describe how to prepare a comprehensive marketing plan and perform this task  satisfying the customer   reading principles of marketing “chapter  customer satisfaction loyalty and empowerment”link principles of marketing “chapter  customer satisfaction loyalty and empowerment” pdf instructions read this chapter which emphasizes customer communities loyalty management customer satisfaction ethics laws and customer empowerment reading this chapter and completing the discussion questions at the end of the chapter should take approximately  hours terms of use the text was adapted by the saylor foundation under the creative commons attributionnoncommercialsharealike  license without attribution as requested by the works original creator or licensee  social marketing   web media youtube steven van hook’s “social marketing”link youtube steven r van hook’s “social marketing” youtube instructions watch this minute video on social marketing most of the tools for promoting commercial projects can also be applied to advancing social causes and programs you may read along with the transcript linked here watching the video taking notes and reviewing the transcript should take approximately  minutes terms of use please respect the copyright and terms of use displayed on the webpages above  cultural modifications for marketing   